desc: "Don't you dare spill anything on this couch"
"Aces of land for you to enjoy"
"What a view to wake up to"
"Cleanse your body and soul in my $5000 tub"
"I bought this entire beach just for you"
"JFK once spilled wine all over this very table"
"This is why I'm charging so much..."
"Yes. That is in fact a mote."
"I bought this island with my first million"
"A lot of people had to die for me to afford this luxury"
